name: Massage-In ni Seiso na Jogakusei ga Kitara? Hame-Ru de Shou!
name_original: Massage-In ni Seiso na Jogakusei ga Kitara? Hame-Ru de Shou!
description:
Massage-In ni Seiso na Jogakusei ga Kitara? Hame-Ru de Shou! is an adventure game developed by miel. It came out on 12-07-2013. It was published by miel.
Massage-In ni Seiso na Jogakusei ga Kitara? Hame-Ru de Shou! is available on PC.
